{
  "stem": "8569.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Since my sister is so very sick-- was so very sick, and she couldn't eat either the bread nor the soup, I used to run to the market and get her, you know, sometimes an apple and sometimes a little bit of sugar, and whatever I could find.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Blockalteste was very, very kind to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The roll calls were going on for hours and hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she used to keep her in the block for the last-- till the last minute and let her go out only when necessary.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in this way, she helped her get over the illness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From that block, we were transferred to another block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I believe it was block number eight, where the union workers were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Before-- the union factory was just being built.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It wasn't ready yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the meantime, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] everybody that was in a Kommando, or in a special department, used to go in the morning for work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And those that weren't assigned stayed in the block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "However, from time to time, they needed people to work around the camp to do whatever cleaning there was to be done.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And nobody wanted to work, so we used to run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I used to hide behind the door-- the front door of the block [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] under a little window where the bread was being stored.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the woman that was responsible for that was always chasing me out of there because they were responsible for the quota of workers to give them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I hated them with a passionate hatred.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This became my very good friend, Marta, whom we got to know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was from Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We became very, very friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And eventually, she saved my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
